      "raw_text": "The Great Northern Co. will en-\nploy negroes hereafter instead of\nJapanese as section hands. Several\ncarloads of negroes have arrived at\nEverett and are being distributed\nalong the line.\n\n\n1t is said to be difficult to secure\nJapanese laborers at present and\nthey do not do as much work as\nother men."
